---
/**
 * Hero — imagem (card 4:5; foto com object-cover preenche o quadro)
 * Grid desktop: texto 7/12 (~58%), figura 5/12 (~42%).
 * Fonte recomendada: ≥1000px no menor lado para nitidez na coluna do hero.
 */
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import heroImage from '../assets/images/heroes/melhores-fogoes-5-bocas-hero.webp';
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-b border-white/10 bg-ink" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-800/40 via-neutral-900/30 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true" />
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-ink via-ink/95 to-brand-900" aria-hidden="true" />
	<div class="absolute -right-20 top-20 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-pop/10 blur-[100px]" aria-hidden="true" />
	<div
		class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-7xl grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-6 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:gap-y-7 lg:min-h-[min(72vh,680px)] lg:items-start lg:gap-x-10 lg:gap-y-7 lg:px-8 lg:py-24"
	>
		<div class="col-span-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 lg:col-span-7 lg:row-start-1">
			<span
				class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-950/30 bg-pop px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-950"
			>
				Atualização 2026
			</span>
			<span class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-on-ink-muted">Decisão de compra · Fogões 5 bocas</span>
		</div>

		<div class="col-span-12 mt-1 max-w-4xl space-y-3 lg:col-span-7 lg:row-start-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:pr-2">
			<h1
				id="hero-heading"
				class="font-display text-2xl font-bold leading-snug tracking-tight text-balance text-on-ink-body md:text-3xl"
			>
				Melhores fogões 5 bocas em 2026: ranking atualizado
			</h1>
			<div class="rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-brand-900/70 p-3.5 ring-1 ring-white/10 sm:p-4">
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-semibold leading-snug text-on-ink-body sm:text-[0.95rem]">
					<li class="text-pop">🥇 Melhor geral: Electrolux FE5IG</li>
					<li class="text-cta">💰 Melhor custo-benefício: Brastemp BFS5NCR</li>
					<li class="text-amber-300">🔥 Mais vendido: Consul CFS5NAB</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-snug text-balance text-on-ink-body md:text-xl">
				Qual o melhor fogão 5 bocas? Veja o fogão 5 bocas mais vendido e compare custo-benefício
			</h2>
		</div>

		<div
			class="col-span-12 max-w-2xl space-y-5 text-base font-normal leading-[1.65] text-on-ink-body sm:text-lg sm:leading-[1.65] lg:col-span-7 lg:row-start-3 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:pr-2"
		>
			<p>Aqui você encontra o que realmente importa para escolher o melhor produto, sem complicação.</p>
			<p>
				Se você busca o <strong class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body">melhor fogão 5 bocas</strong> para a sua rotina, reunimos comparações
				com foco em uso real e <strong class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body">fogão 5 bocas custo-benefício</strong>. Em dúvida entre tamanhos?
				Comece pelo{' '}
				<a
					href="/comparativo-fogao-4-vs-5-bocas"
					class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body underline decoration-pop decoration-2 underline-offset-[0.22em] transition hover:text-pop"
				>
					comparativo entre fogões 4 e 5 bocas
				</a>
				.
			</p>
			<p>
				<span class="select-none" aria-hidden="true">👉 </span>
				<strong class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body">Ofertas atualizadas hoje</strong> — confira preços e <strong class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body">ver disponibilidade</strong> antes que o estoque mude.
			</p>
			<p>
				<span class="select-none" aria-hidden="true">💡 </span>
				Confira agora. Decidir com clareza hoje evita retrabalho amanhã.
			</p>
			<p class="text-base leading-[1.65] text-on-ink-body">
				Quer escolher com mais calma? Veja nosso guia completo sobre{' '}
				<a
					href="/melhor-fogao-5-bocas"
					class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body underline decoration-pop decoration-2 underline-offset-[0.22em] transition hover:text-pop"
				>
					melhor fogão 5 bocas
				</a>
				. Se a ideia é economizar sem complicação, confira também os modelos com{' '}
				<a
					href="/fogao-5-bocas-custo-beneficio"
					class="font-semibold text-on-ink-body underline decoration-pop decoration-2 underline-offset-[0.22em] transition hover:text-pop"
				>
					melhor custo-benefício
				</a>
				.
			</p>
		</div>

		<figure
			class="col-span-12 mx-auto mt-2 w-full max-w-none sm:mt-3 lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-8 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-2 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-0 lg:w-full lg:max-w-none lg:self-start lg:justify-self-stretch lg:pt-0"
		>
			<div
				class="relative mx-auto aspect-[4/5] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/25 bg-brand-900/30 p-1 shadow-[0_32px_64px_-18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.65),0_12px_40px_-20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-white/20 lg:mx-0"
			>
				<span class="absolute inset-1 block w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[0.7rem]">
					<Picture
						src={heroImage}
						alt="Cozinha moderna em tons neutros com fogão a gás de piso preto de cinco bocas, armários cinza e bancada branca."
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						widths={[360, 480, 640, 800, 960, 1200]}
						sizes="(min-width: 1024px) min(50vw, 640px), 100vw"
						quality={82}
						priority
						class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-[60%_32%] md:object-[62%_38%] lg:object-[66%_44%]"
						pictureAttributes={{
							class:
								'absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full [&>img]:h-full [&>img]:w-full [&>img]:scale-100 md:[&>img]:scale-[1.02] lg:[&>img]:scale-[1.03] [&>img]:object-cover [&>img]:object-[60%_32%] md:[&>img]:object-[62%_38%] lg:[&>img]:object-[66%_44%]',
						}}
					/>
				</span>
			</div>
		</figure>

		<div
			class="col-span-12 flex w-full max-w-2xl flex-col gap-4 sm:max-w-none sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:items-stretch sm:gap-4 lg:col-span-7 lg:row-start-4 lg:max-w-none lg:pr-2"
		>
			<a
				href="#top-produtos"
				class="inline-flex min-h-[56px] w-full min-w-0 flex-1 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-white/25 bg-cta px-7 py-4 text-sm font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wide text-white shadow-[0_6px_20px_-4px_rgba(34,197,94,0.55)] ring-2 ring-white/25 transition duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-105 hover:bg-cta-hover hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_-4px_rgba(34,197,94,0.65)] active:scale-[0.98] sm:w-auto sm:min-w-[220px] sm:flex-initial"
				aria-label="Ver melhor preço agora na lista de fogões recomendados"
			>
				🔥 VER MELHOR PREÇO AGORA
			</a>
			<a
				href="#compare-heading"
				class="inline-flex min-h-[56px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-zinc-100 bg-zinc-900 px-7 py-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-on-ink-body shadow-sm ring-1 ring-white/10 transition duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-105 hover:border-zinc-50 hover:bg-zinc-800 hover:text-on-ink-body sm:w-auto"
				aria-label="Comparar modelos de fogão 5 bocas na tabela desta página"
			>
				<span aria-hidden="true">📊 </span>Comparar modelos de fogão
			</a>
		</div>

		<p class="col-span-12 max-w-2xl text-center text-xs leading-relaxed text-on-ink-muted sm:text-left lg:col-span-7 lg:row-start-5 lg:max-w-none lg:pr-2">
			Ofertas atualizadas hoje • Estoque pode variar
		</p>
	</div>
</section>
